title: 14 Arab countries’ ambassadors to China visit Hubei (Wuhan Municipal Government)
text: ( Source : Wuhan Municipal Government ) Ambassadors to China from 14 Arab countries such as Iraq paid a collective visit to the Beidou application project in Optics Valley of Wuhan, capital of central China's Hubei Province , Oct.14 , 2015 .
